i> became quite common in England in the 19th century, when its popularity was influenced in part by  Tennyson's  poem Maud, published in  1855 , but has not been much used since the early decades of the 20th century."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Maud married Giles Orton of Stainton before 1345. They were the parents of at least 3 daughters."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1310–1369":"1310–1369","1345–1414":"1345–1414","1352–Female":"1352–Surnud","1354–Female":"1354–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1414":"1414","before 1345":"enne 1345","1369":"1369","1345":"1345","1354":"1354","1310":"1310","1352":"1352","about 1352":"umbes 1352","abt 1354":"umbes 1354","Cumberland, England":"Cumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1310–1369":"1310–1369","1345–1414":"1345–1414","1352–Female":"1352–Kuollut","1354–Female":"1354–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1414":"1414","before 1345":"ennen vuotta 1345","1369":"1369","1345":"1345","1354":"1354","1310":"1310","1352":"1352","about 1352":"noin 1352","abt 1354":"noin 1354","Cumberland, England":"Cumberland, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1310–1369":"1310–1369","1345–1414":"1345–1414","1352–Female":"1352–Décédée","1354–Female":"1354–Décédée","–Female":"Décédée","1414":"1414","before 1345":"avant 1345","1369":"1369","1345":"1345","1354":"1354","1310":"1310","1352":"1352","about 1352":"environ 1352","abt 1354":"environ 1354","Cumberland, England":"Cumberland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Maud a épousé Giles Orton of Stainton avant 1345. Ils ont eu au moins 3 filles."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1310–1369":"1310–1369","1345–1414":"1345–1414","1352–Female":"1352–Verstorben","1354–Female":"1354–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1414":"1414","before 1345":"vor 1345","1369":"1369","1345":"1345","1354":"1354","1310":"1310","1352":"1352","about 1352":"um 1352","abt 1354":"um 1354","Cumberland, England":"Cumberland, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Maud hat vor 1345 Giles Orton of Stainton gehei